&lt;p&gt;After a banner year for high-profile data breaches in the U.S., Japan, too, is grappling with a similar proliferation of cyber crime, just a few years before &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://oneworldidentity.com/2017/03/08/personal-data-leaks-spike-japan-hampering-cashless-economy-push/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://oneworldidentity.com/2017/03/08/personal-data-leaks-spike-japan-hampering-cashless-economy-push/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CrowdStrike Accelerates Significant Growth and Momentum in APAC Region&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CrowdStrike Inc., the leader in cloud-delivered endpoint protection, today announced triple-digit growth in the Asia Pacific (APAC) region and the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/crowdstrike-accelerates-significant-growth-momentum-210000649.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/crowdstrike-accelerates-significant-growth-momentum-210000649.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The big bank CEOs have agreed to open their account data vaults to fintechs&lt;/h3&gt;
